Yeah.

57:01.217 --> 57:01.457
Okay.

57:01.741 --> 57:10.873
And the students and the artists and all those other Chicanos, their connection to the movement is, oh, we were with Cesar.

57:12.495 --> 57:16.319
Yes, I have a Welga flag.

57:16.339 --> 57:21.726
But that, I mean, that goes back into that kind of question about like the performance, right?

57:21.746 --> 57:22.187
Yeah.

57:22.707 --> 57:26.713
And that comes out of the teatro too, because who the hell was it promoting?

57:27.213 --> 57:30.297
So I'm realizing now that I'm,

57:30.715 --> 57:36.301
Thinking about this and looking back at it that I wasn't like those other Chicanos in El Teatro.

57:36.562 --> 57:37.423
Yeah.

57:37.443 --> 57:37.823
At all.

57:41.908 --> 57:46.252
Because if I was, I would have been over there with Kiki performing in Hollywood.

57:46.673 --> 57:47.534
Yeah.

